<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out this subchapter—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id0c8a3c8e-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80s–3/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> $500,000 for fiscal year 2010; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id0c8a3c8f-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80s–3/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> such sums as may be necessary for each of the fiscal years 2011 through 2014.</content>
</paragraph>
